Package util.searchable

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ISearchableByFilter<T>
    This interfaces defines behavior that allows to filter an object with an ISearchFilter.
    ISearchFilter
    This interface defines a search filter that allows to check whether two objects match or not ( ISearchFilter.searchFilterFunction(Object, Object)).
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ProductCategoryFilter
    Implements the ISearchFilter interface and defines a filter strategy based on the ProductCategory of an IProduct.
    ProductCategoryNodeFilter
    Implements the ISearchFilter interface and defines a filter strategy based on the CategoryTreeNode.getCategory() of an ProductCategoryTreeNode.
    ProductNameFilter
    Implements the ISearchFilter interface and defines a filter strategy based on the name of an IProduct.
    TextSearchIgnoreCaseFilter
    Implements the ISearchFilter interface and defines a filter option based on a String comparison ignoring case differences of an IProduct.
